file.name: path-parameter-validation.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Sample APIs
  version: 1.0.0
  description:
    Sample API

components:
  parameters:
    accountId:
      name: accountId
      schema:
        type: string
      in: path
      required: true

paths:
  /users/{accountId}:
    get:
      operationId: ReadUser
      parameters:
      - $ref: '#/components/parameters/accountId'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 200 response
